{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@M@StoreHelper@objc(cs)AppStoreHelper(im)paymentQueue:updatedTransactions:","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"paymentQueue","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)SKPaymentQueue","text":"SKPaymentQueue","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"updatedTransactions"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SKPaymentTransaction","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)SKPaymentTransaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"}],"symbolKind":"method","platforms":[{"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"beta":false,"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false},{"introducedAt":"12.0","name":"macOS","unavailable":false,"deprecated":false,"beta":false}],"role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"StoreHelper"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"paymentQueue(_:updatedTransactions:)"},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"paymentQueue","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"_","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"queue","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)SKPaymentQueue","text":"SKPaymentQueue"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"updatedTransactions","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"transactions"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)SKPaymentTransaction","text":"SKPaymentTransaction"},{"text":"])","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"queue","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"StoreKit1 payment queue","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"transactions","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Collection of updated transactions (e.g. "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"purchased"},{"type":"text","text":")"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Because our main StoreKit processing is done via StoreKit2 in StoreHelper, all we have to do here is signal to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"StoreKit1 to finish purchased, restored or failed transactions. StoreKit1 purchases are (in theory) immediately"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"available to StoreKit2 (and vice versa), so any purchase will be picked up by StoreHelper as required."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note on subscription transactions: In Xcode StoreKit Testing and Sandbox Testing subscription renewal transactions"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that happen when the app’s not running are NEVER picked up by StoreKit2. That is, the transactions don’t appear","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"code":"StoreKit.Transaction.all","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Transaction.currentEntitlement(for:)"},{"text":". This seems to have been a known issue","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"since the release of StoreKit2 and can lead to the situation where a user has paid to renew their subscription","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"but StoreKit2 has no knowledge of it."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that production builds using the live App Store DO NOT appear to suffer from this issue"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As a workaround, ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"StoreHelper"},{"type":"text","text":" maintains a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"transactionUpdateCache"},{"text":" that keeps track of subscription renewals","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that happen when the app’s not running."}]}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/StoreHelper\/documentation\/StoreHelper\/AppStoreHelper\/paymentQueue(_:updatedTransactions:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/storehelper\/appstorehelper\/paymentqueue(_:updatedtransactions:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Delegate method for the StoreKit1 payment queue. This method handles subscription transactions (e.g. renewals)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that happen when the app’s not running. It also handles in-app purchases made directly from the App Store,","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/StoreHelper\/documentation\/StoreHelper","doc:\/\/StoreHelper\/documentation\/StoreHelper\/AppStoreHelper"]]},"references":{"doc://StoreHelper/documentation/StoreHelper/AppStoreHelper/paymentQueue(_:updatedTransactions:)":{"url":"\/documentation\/storehelper\/appstorehelper\/paymentqueue(_:updatedtransactions:)","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/StoreHelper\/documentation\/StoreHelper\/AppStoreHelper\/paymentQueue(_:updatedTransactions:)","title":"paymentQueue(_:updatedTransactions:)","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"paymentQueue","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SKPaymentQueue","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)SKPaymentQueue"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"updatedTransactions"},{"text":": [","kind":"text"},{"text":"SKPaymentTransaction","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)SKPaymentTransaction"},{"kind":"text","text":"])"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Delegate method for the StoreKit1 payment queue. This method handles subscription transactions (e.g. renewals)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"that happen when the app’s not running. It also handles in-app purchases made directly from the App Store,"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://StoreHelper/documentation/StoreHelper":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"StoreHelper is a Swift Package Manager (SPM) package that enables developers using Xcode 13 - 15 to easily add in-app purchase support to iOS 15 - 17 and macOS 12 - 14 SwiftUI apps."}],"title":"StoreHelper","identifier":"doc:\/\/StoreHelper\/documentation\/StoreHelper","url":"\/documentation\/storehelper","images":[{"identifier":"storehelper-logo.png","type":"icon"}]},"storehelper-logo.png":{"identifier":"storehelper-logo.png","type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/storehelper-logo.png"}],"alt":null},"doc://StoreHelper/documentation/StoreHelper/AppStoreHelper":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"AppStoreHelper"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Support for StoreKit1. Tells the observer that a user initiated an in-app purchase direct from the App Store,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"rather than via the app itself. StoreKit2 does not (yet) provide support for direct purchases, so we need to"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"use StoreKit1. This is a requirement in order to promote in-app purchases on the App Store. If your app doesn’t"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"have a class that implements ","type":"text"},{"code":"SKPaymentTransactionObserver","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and the ","type":"text"},{"code":"paymentQueue(_:updatedTransactions:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"paymentQueue(_:shouldAddStorePayment:for:)"},{"text":" delegate methods then you’ll get an error when you submit the app","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the App Store and you have IAP promotions."}],"url":"\/documentation\/storehelper\/appstorehelper","identifier":"doc:\/\/StoreHelper\/documentation\/StoreHelper\/AppStoreHelper","role":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"AppStoreHelper","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AppStoreHelper"}]}}}